You are my everything, I love you more than anything. Every moment you are in my heart, there is no one I am more connected with. I feel for you always mama♥️

This year I hope you find more love, light, kindness, and happiness in everything you do and everyone you meet. Because that is a reflection of who you are as a person. I hope it surrounds you in all moments. I hope you cherish it and I know we will share some of those moments together. I am looking forwards to that very much so- 

You are brave, with the most courageous heart. I want you to know that this comes from your vulnerability, softness, and sensitivity. This has taught me so much about myself and my own life, thank you for being such a wonderful teacher by example. To me, you are a wonderful mother, friend, teacher, healer, energy, and being. You are a true light. Ill never stop believing this. Continue to be just as you are, you are absolutely the most wonderful person I know. Happy Birthday, ill see you so soon. I can’t wait to squeeze you. I love you mama.
And why does the universe touch your skin, and throw light on you? To see you!
